{"id":375206,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":24}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"群众文化生活(第17期)","column":"","genre":"","count":"288","ytitle":"","mtitle":"里弄居民大闹文化革命","ftitle":"","authors":["宝书"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海杨树浦眉州路居民区大闹文化革命，里弄力学校，里弄彻底扫除文盲，里弄大办托儿所，里弄大搞文化活动，真是一片新气象。这里我们仅仅从几个侧面作了五张速写。你看，真是新气象，新风格，新人物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张楚良　图　宝书　文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\08\\588o050401.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>张楚良</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>这一张图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画的是眉州路的新鲜事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天热也不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋头在创作。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\08\\588o050402.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>红专学校要成立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙坏戏剧组；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶忙排新戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡琴拉起把新剧唱。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\08\\588o050403.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>这些男孩和姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到书本就象看见糖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻了一本又一本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉在那里死不放。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\08\\588o050404.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>可爱的小宝宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过着幸福的生活；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着里弄大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们走进托儿所。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\08\\588o050405.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>‘五天前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伲还是目不识丁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五天后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伲就是小学水平；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不相信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伲写来念给你听。’</FONT>"}]}